{
  "texts": [
    "Setting up an ethics board is not a silver bullet-\"there is no silver bullet\" [35].",
    "Instead, it should be seen as yet another mechanism in a portfolio of mechanisms.",
    "Appendix: Other responsibilitiesIn Section 2, we have listed five responsibilities that existing AI ethics boards have.",
    "But this list was clearly not comprehensive.",
    "An ethics board could also support risk assessments (Appendix A), review the company's risk management practice (Appendix B), or serve as a contact point for whistleblowers (Appendix C)."
  ]
}